tournament.registration_message:
## 🚨 PLEASE READ THESE NOTES FIRST 🚨
> 📝 You can change your information at any time while registration is open.

> ✅ We are collecting first & last names (preferred names encouraged) for badges to enter the NYU facility only. They will not be used elsewhere.

> 📷 Please provide a picture with your face clearly visible, we will need to include these on your badges for ease of access to the NYU facility.

> 💸 We are asking anyone who is able to please contribute ANY AMOUNT to the community support fund. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form 

> ❤️ If you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due.

> 👀 Spectators will not be charged entry but do need to register and receive a lanyard for entry to the NYU facility; fill out the form including the spectator checkbox below and click save info instead of going through payment. 

> 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 If your team's name is not finalized, select Free Agent and return later to create your team. Be sure to check if your team already exists before creating a new one.

> 🧾 We are using Stripe to accept payments. Stripe securely stores your personal data and it will not be used or shared with anyone other than to process the payment.

### If you have any questions, please reach out to Tyler (tyler13) or Alex (bacongames) on Discord!

tournament.registration_message:
## 🚨 PLEASE READ THESE NOTES FIRST 🚨
> 📝 You can change your information at any time while registration is open.

> ✅ We are collecting first & last names (preferred names encouraged) for badges to enter the NYU facility only. They will not be used elsewhere.

> 📷 Please provide a picture with your face clearly visible, we will need to include these on your badges for ease of access to the NYU facility.

> 💸 We are asking anyone who is able to please contribute ANY AMOUNT to the community support fund. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form 

> ❤️ If you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due.

> 👀 Spectators will not be charged entry but do need to register and receive a lanyard for entry to the NYU facility; fill out the form including the spectator checkbox below and click save info instead of going through payment. 

> 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 If your team's name is not finalized, select Free Agent and return later to create your team. Be sure to check if your team already exists before creating a new one.

> 🧾 We are using Stripe to accept payments. Stripe securely stores your personal data and it will not be used or shared with anyone other than to process the payment.

### If you have any questions, please reach out to Tyler (tyler13) or Alex (bacongames) on Discord!

tournament.registration_message:
## 🚨 PLEASE READ THESE NOTES FIRST 🚨
> 📝 You can change your information at any time while registration is open.

> ✅ We are collecting first & last names (preferred names encouraged) for badges to enter the NYU facility only. They will not be used elsewhere.

> 📷 Please provide a picture with your face clearly visible, we will need to include these on your badges for ease of access to the NYU facility.

> 💸 We are asking anyone who is able to please contribute ANY AMOUNT to the community support fund. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form 

> ❤️ If you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due.

> 👀 Spectators will not be charged entry but do need to register and receive a lanyard for entry to the NYU facility; fill out the form including the spectator checkbox below and click save info instead of going through payment. 

> 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 If your team's name is not finalized, select Free Agent and return later to create your team. Be sure to check if your team already exists before creating a new one.

> 🧾 We are using Stripe to accept payments. Stripe securely stores your personal data and it will not be used or shared with anyone other than to process the payment.

### If you have any questions, please reach out to Tyler (tyler13) or Alex (bacongames) on Discord!

tournament.registration_message:
## 🚨 PLEASE READ THESE NOTES FIRST 🚨
> 📝 You can change your information at any time while registration is open.

> ✅ We are collecting first & last names (preferred names encouraged) for badges to enter the NYU facility only. They will not be used elsewhere.

> 📷 Please provide a picture with your face clearly visible, we will need to include these on your badges for ease of access to the NYU facility.

> 💸 We are asking anyone who is able to please contribute ANY AMOUNT to the community support fund. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form 

> ❤️ If you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due.

> 👀 Spectators will not be charged entry but do need to register and receive a lanyard for entry to the NYU facility; fill out the form including the spectator checkbox below and click save info instead of going through payment. 

> 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 If your team's name is not finalized, select Free Agent and return later to create your team. Be sure to check if your team already exists before creating a new one.

> 🧾 We are using Stripe to accept payments. Stripe securely stores your personal data and it will not be used or shared with anyone other than to process the payment.

### If you have any questions, please reach out to Tyler (tyler13) or Alex (bacongames) on Discord!

tournament.registration_message:
## 🚨 PLEASE READ THESE NOTES FIRST 🚨
> 📝 You can change your information at any time while registration is open.

> ✅ We are collecting first & last names (preferred names encouraged) for badges to enter the NYU facility only. They will not be used elsewhere.

> 📷 Please provide a picture with your face clearly visible, we will need to include these on your badges for ease of access to the NYU facility.

> 💸 We are asking anyone who is able to please contribute ANY AMOUNT to the community support fund. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form 

> ❤️ If you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due.

> 👀 Spectators will not be charged entry but do need to register and receive a lanyard for entry to the NYU facility; fill out the form including the spectator checkbox below and click save info instead of going through payment. 

> 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 If your team's name is not finalized, select Free Agent and return later to create your team. Be sure to check if your team already exists before creating a new one.

> 🧾 We are using Stripe to accept payments. Stripe securely stores your personal data and it will not be used or shared with anyone other than to process the payment.

### If you have any questions, please reach out to Tyler (tyler13) or Alex (bacongames) on Discord!

tournament.registration_message:
## 🚨 PLEASE READ THESE NOTES FIRST 🚨
> 📝 You can change your information at any time while registration is open.

> ✅ We are collecting first & last names (preferred names encouraged) for badges to enter the NYU facility only. They will not be used elsewhere.

> 📷 Please provide a picture with your face clearly visible, we will need to include these on your badges for ease of access to the NYU facility.

> 💸 We are asking anyone who is able to please contribute ANY AMOUNT to the community support fund. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form 

> ❤️ If you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due.

> 👀 Spectators will not be charged entry but do need to register and receive a lanyard for entry to the NYU facility; fill out the form including the spectator checkbox below and click save info instead of going through payment. 

> 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 If your team's name is not finalized, select Free Agent and return later to create your team. Be sure to check if your team already exists before creating a new one.

> 🧾 We are using Stripe to accept payments. Stripe securely stores your personal data and it will not be used or shared with anyone other than to process the payment.

### If you have any questions, please reach out to Tyler (tyler13) or Alex (bacongames) on Discord!

Please join us as we celebrate the 10th anniversary of The Brooklyn Coronation! Tournament Festivities will be held on August 9-10, 2025 at the NYU Game Center in downtown Brooklyn. Enjoy the feasts of Chinatown with Richard! Experience endless activities in our beautiful metropolis. 4 cabs

tournament.registration_message:
## 🚨 PLEASE READ THESE NOTES FIRST 🚨
> 📝 You can change your information at any time while registration is open.

> ✅ We are collecting first & last names (preferred names encouraged) for badges to enter the NYU facility only. They will not be used elsewhere.

> 📷 Please provide a picture with your face clearly visible, we will need to include these on your badges for ease of access to the NYU facility.

> 💸 We are asking anyone who is able to please contribute ANY AMOUNT to the community support fund. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form 

> ❤️ If you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due.

> 👀 Spectators will not be charged entry but do need to register and receive a lanyard for entry to the NYU facility; fill out the form including the spectator checkbox below and click save info instead of going through payment. 

> 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 If your team's name is not finalized, select Free Agent and return later to create your team. Be sure to check if your team already exists before creating a new one.

> 🧾 We are using Stripe to accept payments. Stripe securely stores your personal data and it will not be used or shared with anyone other than to process the payment.

### If you have any questions, please reach out to Tyler (tyler13) or Alex (bacongames) on Discord! 

# We can't wait to see you in Brooklyn!
tournament.payment_message: Entry to KQNYC's The Brooklyn Coronation 2024 is $40. We understand some may need financial assistance and have provided an option for those with the ability to to donate a tournament entry amount, as well as an option to chose the amount you donate to the Community Support Fund.
